OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FHealth Correspondent Helen Ford spend
OL,7,Fthe day with Andrew Haley, whose life
OL,8,Fhas changed beyond recognition as a
OL,9,Fresult of Long Covid
OL,11,FLong Covid. It is a condition that did
OL,12,Fnot exist before the pandemic but
OL,13,Fwhich has become all too familiar.
OL,15,FIt is an umbrella term that refers to
OL,16,Fthe wide variety of long term symptoms
OL,17,Fexperienced by some people, months
OL,18,Fafter having Covid-19.
