OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FAs we mark five years since the first
OL,7,FCovid lockdown of March 2020, I was
OL,8,Fkeen to understand how Long Covid is
OL,9,Fstill affecting day-to-day life for
OL,10,Fmany, by spending the day with one
OL,11,FNewcastle man.
OL,13,FMeeting Andrew Haley at his home, he
OL,14,Fis clear that the condition has
OL,15,Fimpacted every aspect of his existence.
OL,17,F"It's like I'm living the life of
OL,18,Fsomebody else," he told me.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/13
