OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FMr Haley's experiences of Long Covid
OL,7,Fgo back several years. He contracted
OL,8,Fthe virus shortly before the initial
OL,9,Flockdown, with longer term symptoms
OL,10,Fkicking in some time later.
OL,12,FThese include fatigue, breathlessness,
OL,13,Fbrain fog and anxiety.
OL,15,FNow, several years on, he described
OL,16,Fhow that crushing fatigue prevents him
OL,17,Fliving the life he once had.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
