OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,F"I wake up after about ten or eleven
OL,7,Fhours sleep and then it's a struggle,"
OL,8,Fhe explained. "That's when the fatigue
OL,9,Fkicks in.
OL,11,F"It's as if an invisible person is
OL,12,Fjust pushing me back on my shoulders,
OL,13,Fback into bed."
OL,15,FPrior to Covid, Mr Haley had been a
OL,16,Fregular at the gym and had worked all
OL,17,Fhis life; often getting up before 5am
OL,18,Ffor his twelve-and-a-half-hour shifts.
OL,20,FThe contrast between then - and now -
OL,21,Fis stark.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/13
