OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,F"I'm thinking," he told me, "how did I
OL,7,Fdo those twelve hour shifts? But they
OL,8,Fwere so easy and now, trying to get
OL,9,Fout of bed, the simplest thing of
OL,10,Fgetting out of bed is harder,
OL,11,Fbasically, than doing a twelve hour
OL,12,Fshift."
OL,14,FAs a result of his symptoms, Mr Haley
OL,15,Fdecided to take early retirement in
OL,16,F2022 and now sees himself as a
OL,17,Fprisoner in his own home.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/13
