OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FHe does not fault the care he has
OL,7,Freceived, first at the Long Covid
OL,8,Fclinic in Newcastle and now, with a
OL,9,Fspecialist who supports him with his
OL,10,Fanxiety.
OL,12,FHowever, Mr Haley believes the country
OL,13,F- more broadly - is no longer giving
OL,14,Fthe issue the attention or investment
OL,15,Fit deserves.
OL,17,FHe told me he feels "cast aside" by a
OL,18,Fsystem that has moved on.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/13
