OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,F"There's a lot more people worse off
OL,7,Fthan me that have long Covid and it's
OL,8,Fessential that we find out," he said.
OL,10,F"Covid brought this country to its
OL,11,Fknees virtually and I just think it's
OL,12,Fbeen swept under the carpet -
OL,13,Fcertainly long Covid."
OL,15,FHow many people are living with Long
OL,16,FCovid?
OL,18,FThe answer is we don't know.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/13
