OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FThere is far less testing for Covid-19
OL,7,Fnow than at the height of the pandemic
OL,8,Fso many people may not realise they
OL,9,Fhave had the virus in the first place.
OL,11,FEven so, the most recent, independent
OL,12,Fsurvey sent to more than two million
OL,13,FGP patients in England provides
OL,14,Fpointers.
OL,16,FIt asked respondents whether they
OL,17,Fwould you describe themselves as
OL,18,Fhaving Long Covid - in other words,
OL,19,Fexperiencing symptoms more than 12
OL,20,Fweeks after an infection that are not
OL,21,Fexplained by something else.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/13
