OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FShe also works on the condition with a
OL,7,Fnumber of other organisations.
OL,9,FDr Duncan says that while patients'
OL,10,Finitial infections are often milder
OL,11,Fnow, the long term impacts can still
OL,12,Fbe devastating.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/13
