OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FShe said: "It can still go on and
OL,7,Fcause Long Covid in a significant
OL,8,Famount of individuals and
OL,9,Funfortunately the research also is
OL,10,Fvery clearly showing us that the more
OL,11,Ftimes you are repeatedly reinfected
OL,12,Fwith Covid, and you can and people
OL,13,Fare, that cumulatively increases your
OL,14,Frisk of developing Long Covid."
OL,16,FDr Duncan continued: "This is our
OL,17,Fworkforce that is being disabled and
OL,18,Fthat's going to have a huge impact not
OL,19,Fonly on the individual and their
OL,20,Ffamily but also on the economy as a
OL,21,Fwhole."
