OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,7,FCare told us it has invested more than
OL,8,F#50m in Long Covid research.
OL,10,FIn a statement it said: "Long Covid
OL,11,Fcan have a debilitating impact on
OL,12,Fpeople's physical and mental health
OL,13,Fand we are committed to ensuring there
OL,14,Fare quality services for people
OL,15,Fsuffering with it in every part of the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,F"No single treatment currently exists
OL,19,Ffor long Covid, which is why we have
OL,20,Ffunded research into the condition."
