OL,3,CHow Long Covid has cast a shadow over
OL,4,Cone man's life
OL,6,FResponsibility for commissioning Long
OL,7,FCovid services now rests with local
OL,8,FIntegrated Care Boards (ICBs).
OL,10,FThe North East and North Cumbria ICB
OL,11,Ftold us: "As part of our commissioning
OL,12,Fplans for this year we are currently
OL,13,Freviewing how services are provided
OL,14,Fwith a view that by autumn we will
OL,15,Fhave a model of care which supports
OL,16,Fthe needs of patients across the
OL,17,Fregion."
